        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Drug Testing for Welfare Recipients Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Temporary Assistance for Needy Families program, the Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program, and specified public housing programs&nbsp;to subject&nbsp;individuals to substance-abuse screening and to deny benefits for individuals who test positive for a controlled substance.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
